{"tid":2298491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Hana妹妹低調做youtuber 外貌似台灣歌手閻亦格","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T13:34:07.000Z","uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0115996a0e55c4b5714a024545f49d12fd858e5","tid":2298491,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uOL41we.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuOL41we.jpg&h=87ad0644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YLi3rFqhPBc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYLi3rFqhPBc&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=7c43c681\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YLi3rFqhPBc</a><br />\n<br />\nTVB星夢歌手菊梓喬（Hana）成長經歷比其他同齡人豐富。因父母離異關係，HANA從小與妹妹相依為命，中三就輟學的她，每日只有返工放工，努力賺錢照顧妹妹。如今妹妹也長大成人，並低調地加入了Youtuber行列。<br />\n<br />\nHANA的妹妹Mianca比菊梓喬細一年，現年33歲。兩人生日相差兩天，而因為從小到大相依為命的關係，感情也相當友好，見到HANA經常在妹妹IG留言。<br />\n<br />\n而HANA在訪問多次提到妹妹，因她努力搵錢，為的是讓妹妹可以讀書，不過妹妹卻因此逃學，最後會考只得2分。雖然如此，但HANA仍然非常愛錫妹妹。<br />\n<br />\n最近Mianca低調做Youtube，為頻道名為「三樓百胃 stomachguchi」，早前在11月11日光棍節發布首條短片《憑實力單身》，Mianca飾演玩交友app的港女。她的外貌打扮與家姐有大不同，家姐偏向清純，而Mianca就比較狂野，從IG的片段所見，Mianca的腿中間到腳跟位置都有一大片紋身。<br />\n<br />\nMianca與家姐都有小虎牙，但外貌反而似台灣歌手閻奕格。首條短片演港女演得入型入格，難怪家姐HANA也大讚妹妹做戲比較叻。"},{"pid":"92a25b77f137cb6f4e1e1468d9529093f8838485","tid":2298491,"uid":56702,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"有無多牙症？"},{"pid":"f7f8f7d466db87be2c173609f407e3d751a437e2","tid":2298491,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92a25b77f137cb6f4e1e1468d9529093f8838485","tid":2298491,"uid":56702,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"有無多牙症？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"睇片就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d76c02aec56b62ca6445caebae5f899ef0221f","tid":2298491,"uid":121504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"呀妹定家姐靚D? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57004dc45c7ee440ef503c2f7169c5146f9d5568","tid":2298491,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d5d76c02aec56b62ca6445caebae5f899ef0221f","tid":2298491,"uid":121504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"呀妹定家姐靚D? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"兩個都靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0c7801a02f8092d59e184c51ddf4085a3cfcdd","tid":2298491,"uid":308873,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ok9UEY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOk9UEY3.png&h=fb7d8898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n格格靚好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e99fe5cde405797e9ff270d7e71410c591eebe","tid":2298491,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d0c7801a02f8092d59e184c51ddf4085a3cfcdd","tid":2298491,"uid":308873,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ok9UEY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOk9UEY3.png&h=fb7d8898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n格格靚好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:24:30.000Z","msg":"原來hana妹仲大過格格三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bdedbbd13ad7f7980c7615b2f95a8917693962","tid":2298491,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"有新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"